nodes.text: Star Wars Insider 135 is the 113th issue of the magazine Star Wars Insider and the 43rd published by Titan Magazines. It was released on July 24, 2012.

Star Wars Insider celebrates 30 years of Star Wars video games from The Empire Strikes Back to The Old Republic. Insider parties on and previews Celebration VI, plus all-new fiction as Insider reveals an exclusive tale with amazing art! There is a complete guide to the X-wing fighter. Also, the latest news on Season Five of Star Wars: The Clone Wars!

This issue came in two covers: the newsstand edition had Darth Vader with Shaak Ti as seen in The Force Unleashed and Darth Malgus from The Old Republic, and the Comic Store Exclusive edition came with Vader looming over an Atari-esque 3D background.
